Web Tools: Bower
-----------------
-> Tools for automation in web development:
a. Bower: Package Manager for the Web;
b. Grunt and Gulp: Task Automation;
c. Yo: Web App Scaffolding;
d. Yeoman: Workflow designed around using Yo, Bower and Grunt;

a. Bower
-------------
Package Manager for the Web;
-> Helps manage dependencies: frameworks, libraries, assets, utilities, etc. that are required for building your web site;
-> e.g., Bootstrap, Font Awesome, JQuery, etc;
-> Fetches all the components required for building the website;
-> Used with the remaining tools in our workflow;
